				<Special>
					<SpecialRuleDescription>Flammable</SpecialRuleDescription>
					<SpecialRuleDescription>Knows only one spell - The Deliverance of Itza: a direct damage spell that targets all enemy units within 12". Each target suffers 2D6 Strength 4 hits. If a target has the Daemonic, Undead or Nehekharan Undead special rule, it suffers 3D6 hits instead</SpecialRuleDescription>
					<SpecialRuleDescription>If Lord Kroak joins a unit of Temple Guard, all models in the combined unit gain the Unbreakable special rule</SpecialRuleDescription>
					<SpecialRuleDescription>Lord Kroak can cast The Deliverance of Itza as many times per turn as he has sufficient power dice</SpecialRuleDescription>
					<SpecialRuleDescription>Lord Kroak's Wizard level can never be reduced to less than 1</SpecialRuleDescription>
